seo: tpshop,SQL注入漏洞,漏洞检测,网络安全
summary: 该插件用于检测tpshop系统是否存在SQL注入漏洞，通过构造特定的payload发送请求并分析响应来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the tpshop system has SQL injection vulnerabilities by constructing specific payloads, sending requests, and analyzing responses to confirm the existence of vulnerabilities.
